[[div class="admohub-about"]]
[[div]]

ADMONITION is a collab-driven anthology portraying a hubristic and starkly totalitarian SCP Foundation attempting to contain the uncontainable, achieve the unachievable, in the name of their mission and in the spirit of their institutional arrogance.

Each installment, featuring a preordained volunteer author, aims to explore a unique aspect of the SCP universe and its relationship to the series' themes. New episodes are periodically released according to an overarching plan; the series will end with a total of ten episodes plus a number of complementary articles.

= @@ @@

The series is primarily set in a split timeline branching from that of the [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/site-17-hub |Site-17 Deepwell Catalog]]] canon; characters, SCPs, and other elements may be borrowed from the setting without total adherence to their original counterparts.

